e Compology client saves $1,800 per dumpster per year, or about 30% of waste collection costs.<\/p>\n                                                                                <p><a class=\"text-primary\" href=\"\/solutions\/automated-rightsizing\/\">Explore automated rightsizing<\/a><\/p>\n                                        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"two-col-component mx-md-5 mx-sm-1 mx-xs-1 mx-lg-5 mx-xl-5\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row d-none d-md-flex pt-5 pb-5\">\n                        <div class=\" col-lg col-xl col-md  d-flex position-relative\">\n                <p class=\"h1\">Hauler Partnership<\/p>\n                                <h2>VERIFY SERVICE EVENTS AND IDENTIFY SERVICE TREND CHANGES<\/h2>\n                                                        <p>Verifiable data and images let you understand if service levels are being met according to contracts in place, and partner with your haulers to regularly review service schedules based on actual waste outputs.<\/p>\n                                                    <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-7 offset-xl-1 img-col\">\n                                <div class=\"image-holder \">\n                    <img class=\"img-fluid lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/compology.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/Web-image-Missed-Service-Summary-4.png\" alt=\"Hauler Partnership\" \/>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"d-block d-md-none mobile-content mt-4\">\n            <div class=\"row mb-4\">\n                <div class=\"col-12\">\n                                        <div class=\"image-holder \">\n                        <img class=\"img-fluid lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/compology.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/Web-image-Missed-Service-Summary-4-810x540.png\" alt=\"Hauler Partnership\" \/>\n                    <\/div>\n                                                                                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"col-12\">\n                    <p class=\"h1\">Hauler Partnership<\/p>\n                    <h2>VERIFY SERVICE EVENTS AND IDENTIFY SERVICE TREND CHANGES<\/h2>\n                                                    <p>Verifiable data and images let you understand if service levels are being met according to contracts in place, and partner with your haulers to regularly review service schedules based on actual waste outputs.<\/p>\n                                                                                <p><a class=\"text-primary\" href=\"\"><\/a><\/p>\n                                        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"two-col-component mx-md-5 mx-sm-1 mx-xs-1 mx-lg-5 mx-xl-5\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row d-none d-md-flex pt-5 pb-5\">\n                        <div class=\"col-xl-7 col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-6 img-col\">\n                                <div class=\"image-holder \">\n                    <img class=\"img-fluid lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/compology.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/Contamination_Graphic-1-1620x1080.png\" alt=\"Contamination Reduction\" \/>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md col-lg col-xl-4 offset-xl-1  d-flex position-relative\">\n                <p class=\"h1\">Contamination Reduction<\/p>\n                                <h2>Avoid fines and improve diversion practices<\/h2>\n                                                        <p>Our AI-powered waste metering technology automatically scans images to identify 6+ categories of contamination. Through email alerts, text alerts and reporting, we educate you on which material should go in each bin so you can avoid fines and improve recycling practices and diversion from landfill.<\/p>\n                                                                            <p><a class=\"text-primary\" href=\"\/solutions\/contamination-reduction\/\">Explore contamination reduction<\/a><\/p>\n                                            <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"d-block d-md-none mobile-content mt-4\">\n            <div class=\"row mb-4\">\n                <div class=\"col-12\">\n                                                                                    <div class=\"image-holder \">\n                        <img class=\"img-fluid lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/compology.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/Contamination_Graphic-1-810x540.png\" alt=\"Contamination Reduction\" \/>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <\/div>\n                <div class=\"col-12\">\n                    <p class=\"h1\">Contamination Reduction<\/p>\n                    <h2>Avoid fines and improve diversion practices<\/h2>\n                                                    <p>Our AI-powered waste metering technology automatically scans images to identify 6+ categories of contamination. Through email alerts, text alerts and reporting, we educate you on which material should go in each bin so you can avoid fines and improve recycling practices and diversion from landfill.<\/p>\n                                                                                <p><a class=\"text-primary\" href=\"\/solutions\/contamination-reduction\/\">Explore contamination reduction<\/a><\/p>\n                                        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"two-col-component mx-md-5 mx-sm-1 mx-xs-1 mx-lg-5 mx-xl-5\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row d-none d-md-flex pt-5 pb-5\">\n                        <div class=\" col-lg col-xl col-md  d-flex position-relative\">\n                <p class=\"h1\">Sustainability &amp; ESG<\/p>\n